These are a perfect size, and you can have them straight, diluted, hot, cold, doctored with herbs or whatever into a sort of soup; they are extremely versatile. My understanding is that they are predominantly tomato juice made from fully ripened specially grown tomatoes right at the source where this product is made, which I think you can taste; and the rest is a mixture of other vegetables. On top of that they are affordable and seem to hold up well in storage. Overall I think this is a great product.
